{"tid":548663,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（懷念爺爺）多唔多人屋企仲有家居電話","createTime":"2018-02-02T19:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T23:19:11.000Z","uid":28736,"like":32,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e6fd4061103785eaf6bb9d301f78089fef9d2008","tid":548663,"uid":28736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T19:53:04.000Z","msg":"已經無用家居電話5,6年到 <br />\n今日突然諗起細個夜晚一定同fd煲電話粥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好深刻我個電話係無線 成日傾到無電 要轉手機傾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小學雞老母交電話費 有次爆分鐘爆到上網check我同咩號碼傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實晚晚都傾 唔知有乜撚傾都晚晚傾到夜一夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打機更加唔使講 一定係用膊頭夾住 打幾個鐘膊頭都痛埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前仲會玩3line 要好有規矩咁 有得駁線既互call左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以駁到4,5條友一齊傾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有家居電話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經無家居電話"},{"pid":"b4f9ba7c7778e7df31f2fe0c05e4091664823194","tid":548663,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T19:54:21.000Z","msg":"孫中山"},{"pid":"461b39e0e5b9de5462edff950f59906d6953cb49","tid":548663,"uid":124869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T20:01:28.000Z","msg":"屋企有兩個無線電話<br />\n打機個陣 一個無電即換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca7a6933eb4d015f294535bf6e96c10807e34d7","tid":548663,"uid":1312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T20:29:09.000Z","msg":"投你老母票咩"},{"pid":"b88e7104069f2da069087cdf1af63fd8488f2430","tid":548663,"uid":19072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T21:39:54.000Z","msg"